name: Customised Levis

We have a range of fabrics which we can customise your levis with or maybe you fancy some studs!? Whatever you fancy - let us know! We have fabrics such as snakeskin, leopard print, camouflage, american flag, galaxy print and floral. Please email therework@gmail.com once you have paid for your item to discuss exactly what you would like. - please include a paypal reference ID so we can track your payment. *These items are made to order so please allow up to 10 working days for your items to be customised* PLEASE NOTE THESE LEVIS ARE NON REFUNDABLE AS THEY ARE MADE SPECIFICALLY TO YOUR ORDER.
